    d?
        Tablet computer ->^{URL} DNS server ->^{IP address} ->  Tablet computer ->^{Request for web page} Web server with that IP address ->^{Web page} Browser on Tablet computer, which displays the web page
    e?
        The web browser asks the web server to identify itself. The web server sends back its digital certificate. The hypertext transfer protocol authenticates the digital certificate. If it is authentic, encrypted data transmission begins.
